971
00:45:02.040 --> 00:45:03.330
<font color="#ffffff">Und eine Angstmacherei.</font>

972
00:45:03.320 --> 00:45:04.890
<font color="#ffffff">(Philipp Gut) Reine Propaganda.</font>

973
00:45:04.860 --> 00:45:07.130
<font color="#ffffff">(Adrian Amstutz) Herr Jositsch, das</font>
